Closes: #13829

The problem with the current implementation is that the function reads only the first _calculated from Math.min_ bytes of the string. UTF-8 can have characters that consist of more than 2 bytes. JS character is a 2-byte size.

In this implementation, there is a high probability of reading only part of the character. This is something like:
```ts
